review:
From looking at the trailer I found the game to look so wacky. What drawed me in was the grappling mechanics. And let me just say, this game is absolutely fun. The mechanics are weirdly enough complicated. Complicated enough for it to take me at least 8 hours of gaming to fully understand it. And let me just say I'm preeeety dumb. Anyways because of this game I fell in love with the series and hope to master the rest. ;-;

P.S. The soundtrack goes hard.

9/10
